Didn&#x27;t know about setting DH parameters.<p>On each server, do the following:<p><pre><code>    sudo openssl dhparam -out /etc/nginx/ssl/dhparam.pem 2048
</code></pre>
Then in nginx.conf set:<p><pre><code>    http {
        ssl_dhparam /etc/nginx/ssl/dhparam.pem;
    }</code></pre>
